33316\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2843435\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"1164\\\" data-end=\\\"1317\\\">Sim. Manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o an\\u00f4nima \\u00e9 permitida, mas, nesses casos, o acompanhamento e retorno poder\\u00e3o ser limitados.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"f550ab4\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f566df0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>O prazo pode variar conforme o tipo de manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o, mas normalmente a resposta \\u00e9 dada em at\\u00e9 <strong data-start=\\\"1486\\\" data-end=\\\"1497\\\">30 dias<\\/strong>, prorrog\\u00e1vel conforme a complexidade do caso.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"8721b34\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"25b87b4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"1545\\\" data-end=\\\"1730\\\">Sim. Ao finalizar o envio, voc\\u00ea receber\\u00e1 um n\\u00famero de protocolo para acompanhar o andamento e a resposta no pr\\u00f3prio sistema.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"42927e8\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a2f727e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"1732\\\" data-end=\\\"1950\\\">N\\u00e3o. Ap\\u00f3s o envio, a manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o n\\u00e3o pode ser alterada. Caso necess\\u00e1rio, uma nova manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o pode ser registrada com as informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es complementares.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"18674b3\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"aa4575c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"1952\\\" data-end=\\\"2121\\\">Voc\\u00ea receber\\u00e1 um n\\u00famero de protocolo como confirma\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Esse n\\u00famero comprova o registro e permite o acompanhamento.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"def692b\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"02dc0fa\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"2123\\\" data-end=\\\"2351\\\">N\\u00e3o. A ouvidoria n\\u00e3o tem fun\\u00e7\\u00e3o jur\\u00eddica e n\\u00e3o substitui advogados ou processos legais. Seu papel \\u00e9 institucional, visando \\u00e0 melhoria dos servi\\u00e7os.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"b7cc5c9\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3159792\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"2353\\\" data-end=\\\"2597\\\">N\\u00e3o. O atendimento ao cidad\\u00e3o presta informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es e servi\\u00e7os. A ouvidoria atua de forma <strong data-start=\\\"2511\\\" data-end=\\\"2538\\\">mediadora e estrat\\u00e9gica<\\/strong>, recebendo manifesta\\u00e7\\u00f5es para an\\u00e1lise e melhoria cont\\u00ednua.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"e12c4d8\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1587766\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p data-start=\\\"2599\\\" data-end=\\\"2823\\\">Sim. O sistema adota medidas de seguran\\u00e7a e segue a <strong data-start=\\\"2731\\\" data-end=\\\"2772\\\">Lei Geral de Prote\\u00e7\\u00e3o de Dados (LGPD)<\\/strong> para garantir a confidencialidade das informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"e084170\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a61fd0f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Sim. A ouvidoria atua de forma transversal e pode encaminhar manifesta\\u00e7\\u00f5es para os setores competentes de acordo com o assunto.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"ce187e4\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3fa486e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Sim. O sistema permite anexar arquivos que auxiliem na an\\u00e1lise da manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o, como fotos, documentos e comprovantes.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"210f2c2\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9473702\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>A manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9 analisada e encaminhada ao setor respons\\u00e1vel. A ouvidoria acompanha o tratamento e garante que voc\\u00ea receba uma resposta.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"d83f3a2\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9a1ad13\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>A equipe da ouvidoria realiza a triagem inicial e encaminha ao setor competente. Em alguns casos, pode haver contato direto para esclarecimentos.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"c592c76\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cb56162\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>A ouvidoria recebe manifesta\\u00e7\\u00f5es da sociedade. J\\u00e1 a corregedoria atua internamente, com foco em apura\\u00e7\\u00e3o disciplinar de condutas de servidores p\\u00fablicos.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"27210f7\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"905b305\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Depende da institui\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Verifique se h\\u00e1 outros canais de atendimento dispon\\u00edveis al\\u00e9m do sistema digital.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"d6c4b46\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9229537\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Voc\\u00ea pode registrar uma <strong data-start=\\\"4115\\\" data-end=\\\"4145\\\">manifesta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de reitera\\u00e7\\u00e3o<\\/strong> ou <strong data-start=\\\"4149\\\" data-end=\\\"4160\\\">recurso<\\/strong> no pr\\u00f3prio sistema, solicitando nova an\\u00e1lise.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true},{\"id\":\"d934a5d\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"_title\":\"item N\\u00ba2\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d863064\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Sim. O sistema de ouvidoria digital pode ser acessado <strong data-start=\\\"4316\\\" data-end=\\\"4338\\\">a qualquer momento<\\/strong>, todos os dias da semana.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true,\"isLocked\":true}]}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
